# Hello World (KC13)

Two `scalascript` blocks and `${ident}` interpolation — both must survive the pipeline.

```scalascript
def greet(name: String): String = s"Hello, ${name}!"
```

```scalascript
def main(): Unit = println(greet("World"))
```
